Trapped In a Haunted Psychiatric Ward | Ravenswood | Full Horror Movie

When four American tourists - Sofia, Carl, Belle and Michael - go on a ghost tour, they get much more than they bargained for, when the spirits of an evil doctor and his last victim trap them in an old abandoned psychiatric ward.

2017.  Stars: Madeline Marie Dona, Jock Campbell, Shane Savage
